<div id="stripe">Subscribe to the Perl Weekly</div>

<div>
    <p>
     In order to subscribe to the newsletter send an email
     to Gabor: <b>gabor@szabgab.com</b> with a subject: <b>Subscribe to Perl Weekly</b>.
    <p>
     I know that for most newsletters you just subscribe almost anonymously, but I'd like to know a bit about the readers of the newsletter.
    <p>
     Please include your name and where did you read about the Perl Weekly? What made you subscribe now?<br>
     I would also love to hear about you: How long have you been using Perl? What do you do with Perl? Where do you work?<br>
     If you have a website or a blog, please also include a link to it. If you use LinkedIn, please include a link to your profile.
    </p>
</div>


